remember to stay in your lane

00:04:13.229 --> 00:04:15.580
and I think that's a good way to conceive

00:04:15.580 --> 00:04:20.458
how to think about grammatical person

00:04:20.458 --> 00:04:23.615
is if you start in one lane,

00:04:25.665 --> 00:04:28.230
don't cross over by the
end of the sentence.

00:04:28.230 --> 00:04:32.198
Begin, begin your sentence in
the same lane as you started.

